General.Name: Kreate Group Oyj
General.Description: Kreate Group Oyj engages in the construction of infrastructure projects for private and public sector customers in Finland. It offers bridge construction and repair, rock construction, and circular economy, and expert services, as well as foundation and concrete, railway, fairway, special foundation construction, and environmental construction services. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Tuusula, Finland.
